title: HonSine Key Organizer&Keychain Compact Keyholder with PU Leather Keychain
features: STURDY BUT LIGHT! - HonSine key holder is made out of top quality carbon and the bolts, accessories are crafted from stainless steel. All these are making it a lightweight and durable key organizer.
PATENTED DESIGN - Our HonSine Keyholder is patented and comes with a modern, stylish look suitable for men or women in search of a smart way to hold their keys. A tool to enjoy for many years.

A GIFT FOR TWO - The organizer comes stylishly packed in a gift box together with an extra keychain suitable for more keys or the car key. This way you can also make someone else happy no matter the occasion: birthdays, Thanksgiving, Father's day or even Christmas.
GOODBYE, BULKY POCKETS!! - A compact keyholder that frees up you pocket by keeping all your keys organized and quiet. No more pocking and jigling! Designed for your comfort, because comfort is key!

HUGE SET-EASY TO ASSEMBLE- SPECIAL ACCESSORIES - Equipped with daily neccesities such as a shopping cart unlocker, that can be removed after unlocking, a sim card tray pin and a bottle opener. The oranizer is easy to assemble, you can use the provided screwdriver or just a coin! The holder kit includes everything you need. To make everything even more simple you can watch our video for more information.
